==食物配搭==
最常見的貴腐酒搭配食物為鵝肝、[[藍乾酪|藍乾酪]]及少數種類的堅果。然而貴腐酒須注意避免和可可含量高的巧克力、咖啡等食物一起食用。<ref name="info" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=【葡萄酒款】貴腐酒，產區、風味、經典搭餐全攻略|url=https://www.winentaste.com/magazine/special_botrytis|accessdate=2020-10-26|work=WINE&TASTE 品迷網|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028204849/https://www.winentaste.com/magazine/special_botrytis|dead-url=no}}</ref>

